#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn5.8"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn5.8:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 5 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 5 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn5.8:0.2"
msgid "1. Bhikkhunīvagga "
msgstr "1. Nuns "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn5.8:0.3"
msgid "8. Sīsupacālāsutta "
msgstr "8. With Sīsupacālā "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts2ed1.293, sc1
msgctxt "sn5.8:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. VAR: sīsupacālā → sīsūpacālā (bj)
msgctxt "sn5.8:1.2"
msgid "Atha kho sīsupacālā bhikkhunī pubbaṇhasamayaṃ nivāsetvā … pe … "
msgstr "Then the nun Sīsupacālā robed up in the morning … "

msgctxt "sn5.8:1.3"
msgid "aññatarasmiṃ rukkhamūle divāvihāraṃ nisīdi. "
msgstr "and sat at the root of a tree for the day’s meditation. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn5.8:1.4"
msgid "Atha kho māro pāpimā yena sīsupacālā bhikkhunī tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā sīsupacālaṃ bhikkhuniṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "Then Māra the Wicked went up to Sīsupacālā and said to her, "

msgctxt "sn5.8:1.5"
msgid "“kassa nu tvaṃ, bhikkhuni, pāsaṇḍaṃ rocesī”ti? "
msgstr "“Nun, whose creed do you believe in?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn5.8:1.6"
msgid "“Na khvāhaṃ, āvuso, kassaci pāsaṇḍaṃ rocemī”ti. "
msgstr "“I don’t believe in anyone’s creed, sir.” "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn5.8:2.1"
msgid "“Kaṃ nu uddissa muṇḍāsi, "
msgstr "“In whose name did you shave your head? "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn5.8:2.2"
msgid "Samaṇī viya dissasi; "
msgstr "You look like an ascetic, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn5.8:2.3"
msgid "Na ca rocesi pāsaṇḍaṃ, "
msgstr "but you don’t believe in any creed. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn5.8:2.4"
msgid "Kimiva carasi momūhā”ti. "
msgstr "Why do you live as if lost?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "sn5.8:3.1"
msgid "“Ito bahiddhā pāsaṇḍā, "
msgstr "“Followers of other creeds "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn5.8:3.2"
msgid "diṭṭhīsu pasīdanti te; "
msgstr "are confident in their views. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn5.8:3.3"
msgid "Na tesaṃ dhammaṃ rocemi, "
msgstr "But I don’t believe in their teaching, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn5.8:3.4"
msgid "te dhammassa akovidā. "
msgstr "for they’re no experts in the Dhamma. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts1ed1.134, pts2ed1.294, sc4
msgctxt "sn5.8:4.1"
msgid "Atthi sakyakule jāto, "
msgstr "But there is one born in the Sakyan clan, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn5.8:4.2"
msgid "buddho appaṭipuggalo; "
msgstr "the unrivaled Buddha, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn5.8:4.3"
msgid "Sabbābhibhū māranudo, "
msgstr "champion, dispeller of Māra, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn5.8:4.4"
msgid "sabbatthamaparājito. "
msgstr "everywhere undefeated, "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc5
msgctxt "sn5.8:5.1"
msgid "Sabbattha mutto asito, "
msgstr "everywhere freed, and unattached, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn5.8:5.2"
msgid "sabbaṃ passati cakkhumā; "
msgstr "the all-seeing seer. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn5.8:5.3"
msgid "Sabbakammakkhayaṃ patto, "
msgstr "He has attained the end of all deeds, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn5.8:5.4"
msgid "vimutto upadhisaṅkhaye; "
msgstr "freed with the ending of attachments. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn5.8:5.5"
msgid "So mayhaṃ bhagavā satthā, "
msgstr "That Blessed One is my Teacher, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn5.8:5.6"
msgid "tassa rocemi sāsanan”ti. "
msgstr "and I believe in his instruction.” "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p>
#. REF: sc6
msgctxt "sn5.8:6.1"
msgid "Atha kho māro pāpimā “jānāti maṃ sīsupacālā bhikkhunī”ti dukkhī dummano tatthevantaradhāyīti. "
msgstr "Then Māra the Wicked, thinking, “The nun Sīsupacālā knows me!” miserable and sad, vanished right there."

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
